# Tech Stack

## TypeScript
- Always use TypeScript (`.ts` for logic, `.tsx` for components) — never plain `.js` or `.jsx`
- All new files must be TypeScript

## Tailwind CSS
- Use Tailwind CSS for all styling — no CSS modules, styled-components, or inline `style` objects
- This project uses Tailwind CSS v4 with `@tailwindcss/postcss`
- Global styles live in `src/app/globals.css`
